&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The summary for this role is:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To be one of the senior clinician’s representing Circle Integrated Care in the Hampshire in GP and remote settings.&lt;/p&gt;
